## Free Identity verification KYC

1. Run application (python>=3.8):
```sh
# Deploy MongoDB and Redis queue
docker-compose up -d

# install package
pip3 install -r requirements.txt

# Deploy face recognition model
python3 gateway.py

# Deploy backend api
python3 main.py
```

2. Run API:
- Register (4.1):

`Method`: POST

`Content-Type`: application/json
